  <div class="paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--view-mode--mega-menu paragraph--181386">
          
        
                    <p>The Cato Institute has released its <a href="https://www.cato.org/annualreport23">2023 Annual Report</a> documenting a dynamic year of growth and productivity, as well as our exciting plans for future impact. The digital Annual Report takes you on a virtual journey though the stories within this publication and will give you an inside look into how we’re amplifying our ideas, influence, and impact.</p>
            
